{"tid":979934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"千萬網美女神  ２３分鐘不雅影片流出！鏡頭前露胸開腿自摸好激烈！","createTime":"2019-01-13T06:20:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T06:35:00.000Z","uid":212399,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c49725ada7a132ad286dc1bb40213c2997d05e16","tid":979934,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T06:20:02.000Z","msg":"墨西哥一名 28 歲的人氣 YouTuber&nbsp;「 CaELiKe 」，開朗又火辣的她頗受歡迎，光是頻道訂閱人數就超過&nbsp;1400 萬人，社群網站粉絲人數更是高達 690 多萬名，不過最近網路上卻瘋傳一支疑似 CaELiKe 的私密影片，掀起軒然大波。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.clickme.net/gallery/a995c8a98405dafafeadaa470e4b64ef.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.clickme.net%2Fgallery%2Fa995c8a98405dafafeadaa470e4b64ef.jpeg&h=89eacb90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.clickme.net/gallery/485b85b05582d02e5eabfb9348970aaa.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.clickme.net%2Fgallery%2F485b85b05582d02e5eabfb9348970aaa.jpeg&h=8d9d8445&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.clickme.net/gallery/cdaf9ed0824dbe8f9bb741b82168bcfe.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.clickme.net%2Fgallery%2Fcdaf9ed0824dbe8f9bb741b82168bcfe.jpeg&h=c6930b3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這支私密影片長度23分鐘，內容是她對著鏡頭自慰的影片，只見她撩起上衣露出雙乳，還大開雙腿自摸中洞，甚至還開「後門」給人看透透，影片一出引起熱烈討論，網友對比之後認為很可能就是同一人。<br />\n事發至今，CaELiKe仍然未對影片做出回應。CaELiKe一直帶給大眾健康活潑的形象，分享美妝教學更是讓她受到女粉歡迎，因此女粉絲對此紛紛抱不平，認為這都是正常不過的行為，猜測一定是有心人士意圖摧毀她的形象才惡意流出。<br />\n<a href=\"http://clickme.net/43588\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fclickme.net%2F43588&d=cNQCUWuAuUgGHXOevH1H0NibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=318d4801\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://clickme.net/43588</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89343d3bb9a8c583059ffbfc4f706f2e63ed6596","tid":979934,"uid":26711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T06:20:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef549b7ed4b40e4422047c9a62943f5dcba79ac2","tid":979934,"uid":211,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T06:20:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c881dc3c05931035a0cfde8df02ac7a9f9f010","tid":979934,"uid":174150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T06:20:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"644bf54d00cdd5a85daa09711a931f1c58d61e7a","tid":979934,"uid":34562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T06:21:04.000Z","msg":"唉，唔講啦"},{"pid":"9c45c10eec9e643c8fd45bd51bd1466886fda5f6","tid":979934,"uid":175661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T06:21:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35fc29950dd57659e4317ca2c4dccb106e59a87e","tid":979934,"uid":13467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T06:21:16.000Z","msg":"樓上班仆街仔"},{"pid":"c743bc33d9445405d25edafdbb8a6826cb12b4bc","tid":979934,"uid":136735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T06:21:37.000Z","msg":"一入已經無得睇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4dae3c67ace533093301cfca7ce059cf7295515","tid":979934,"uid":30098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T06:22:08.000Z","msg":"屌 嬲"},{"pid":"25d920d1ab9086ff72f7f6e813317eb8e577ca13","tid